<section aria-labelledby="preview-heading" class="my-12">
  <h2 id="preview-heading">What's inside the kit</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-ink-muted">
    A focused operational PDF — instant download after purchase. Eight sections, in the order you'll use them.
  </p>
  <ol class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
    {
      sections.map((s) => (
        <li class="rounded-md border border-border bg-surface-elevated p-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary">{s.label}</p>
          <p class="mt-1 font-semibold text-ink-heading">{s.title}</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-snug text-ink">{s.body}</p>
        </li>
      ))
    }
  </ol>
  <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-ink-muted">
    PDF is print-friendly and readable on a phone, tablet, or printed and taken to the bank.
  </p>
</section>
